snippet.title: The YouTube Rub
snippet.description:
A collection of audio clips by the team on the Melbourne Triple M Footy Rub. Predominantly the Saturday Rub, used to include the Friday Rub and have dabbled in some Midweek and Sunday Rubs. 

I edit out the boring bits and leave just the funniest parts of an entire broadcast. 

Currently featuring James "JB" Brayshaw, Brian "BT" Taylor, Bernie Vince, Wayne "Duck" Carey, Billy "Fat" Brownless, "Purple-Headed Warrior" Damian Barrett, Ash "The Chu Man" Chua and special guest appearances from Jason "The Chief" Dunstall. 

Past participants have been "The Lonewolf" Garry Lyon, Danny "Spud Regal" Frawley, "Chief" Jason Dunstall, Sam "Fossil" Newman, "Duke" Luke Darcy, Mark "Stevo" Stevens, "Crawf" Shane Crawford, "Hammer" Hamish McLachlan. Wayne "Schwatta" Schwass, Mark "Howie" Howard and Michael Christian. 

I own none of the content. It all belongs to Southern Cross Austereo. I just upload the brilliance.
